history.proof: intros [f Hf]. exists (fun n => match n with | 0 => Some None | S n' => option_map Some (f n') end). intros [x |]. - destruct (Hf x) as [n Hn]. exists (S n). rewrite Hn. reflexivity. - exists 0. reflexivity.
